Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,STOCKROOM. AI-augmented inventory control management for the supply\NNCO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: 5,000 items, disconnected Excel docs, no relational\Nview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Five thousand items in scope. Filter by location, category, custodian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Top metrics surface inventory-overdue and NMC-impacting counts\Nimmediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Type a question in plain English. The AI engine parses it into a JSON\Nfilter spec.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Visible parsed spec — no SQL, no opaque magic. Then it runs against\Nthe table.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero model drafts a Readiness and Lateral Transfer Brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,BLUF, overdue counts, NMC shortages, sensitive-item flags, three\Nactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Three clicks: pick a scenario, surface the gaps, copy actions to the\Nstandup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs inside the wire. IL5 /\NIL6 ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
